@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@token =
### ================== PARADAS DE RUTA ==================

### Obtener todas las paradas asignadas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/route-stops
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Crear una parada para una ruta
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/route-stops
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "routeId": 1,
  "stopId": 1,
  "position": 1,
  "scheduledTimeHint": "07:10:00",
  "status": "ACTIVO"
}

###

### Obtener parada de ruta por IDs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/route-stops/1/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Actualizar parada de ruta
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/route-stops/1/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "position": 2,
  "scheduledTimeHint": "07:20:00",
  "status": "ACTIVO"
}

###

### Eliminar parada de ruta físicamente
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/route-stops/1/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Eliminar parada de ruta lógicamente
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/route-stops/1/1/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
